data.description: Welcome to this very spacious home in the Verrado Community! This home features neutral tile throughout the house, with an open concept floor plan, gorgeous in-eat kitchen with granite countertops and even a breakfast nook area! The upstairs has a big loft. Walking into the master bedroom, you are greeted with a gorgeous space that includes a big walk-in closet and a huge bathroom with a tub to relax in. The upstairs is where you will also find the 3 additional generously-sized bedrooms. The backyard includes a cozy patio with a large canvas to create your dream backyard. The owner has installed a NEW reverse osmosis system, new irrigation, and new flooring in the kitchen. The home also has OWNED SOLAR PANELS!!
